  "note": [
    {
      "text": "Bilateral knee pain worsening over 2-3 months, mechanical pattern. Exam: mild crepitus bilaterally, no effusion, full extension, flexion to 120 degrees, stable ligaments, non-antalgic gait. Consistent with early degenerative osteoarthritis. Started naproxen 250 mg BID PRN. Counseled on weight management and low-impact exercise."
